  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/320e35b207014ad99b4543c5f36b45b6.avif?t=1750723827\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras_big/320e35b207014ad99b4543c5f36b45b6.avif?t=1750723827 width=800 height=130 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Kill the Skeletons</strong> – <i>Embrace the Chaos!</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to fight the undead? <strong>Kill the Skeletons</strong> is a <strong>3D clicker battle</strong> where thousands of creatures fly across the battlefield, and hundreds of weapons unleash pure destruction!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Tap to Attack, Obliterate the Horde!</i></strong><br>Your reflexes and weapons are your greatest tools. Click to destroy waves of skeletons, buy more weapons and enjoy the chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/ebf19bf90ee4768db0b5c084e7a1abaf.poster.avif?t=1750723827\" width=640 height=273 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/ebf19bf90ee4768db0b5c084e7a1abaf.webm?t=1750723827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Thousands of Skeletons, Increasingly Tougher Star Levels!</i></strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt down thousands of skeletons and take on tougher star-level skeletons that are harder to kill but reward you with tons of gold! Grow your fortune and become unstoppable!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/e0f526871d31e990e8d48a45357daef2.poster.avif?t=1750723827\" width=640 height=273 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/e0f526871d31e990e8d48a45357daef2.webm?t=1750723827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Over 10 Unique Weapons</i></strong><br>From swords and magic casters to laser runes and giant mortars, each weapon has its own mechanics and stunning visual effects!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/253814a39fcfc915d96c7db51f25f99b.poster.avif?t=1750723827\" width=640 height=273 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/253814a39fcfc915d96c7db51f25f99b.webm?t=1750723827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Unlimited Upgrades</i></strong><br>There’s no limit to your power! <strong>Upgrade your weapons and combine them for greater star level weapons </strong>to take on even larger enemy swarms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/8609de668dbea0c89c7cabfed06ea548.poster.avif?t=1750723827\" width=640 height=273 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/8609de668dbea0c89c7cabfed06ea548.webm?t=1750723827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Mini-Games & Permanent Upgrades</strong>!<br>The fun never stops! Play mini-games to earn rewards and unlock <strong>permanent upgrades</strong> for an even stronger start each time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Three Different Currencies, Three Unique Strategies</strong><br>Each currency has its own mechanics and upgrade paths, allowing you to customize your playstyle and maximize your power.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀💀💀 <br>The skeleton war is about to begin! <strong>Grab your weapons, control the chaos, and dominate the battlefield!</strong> <br>💀💀💀</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/320e35b207014ad99b4543c5f36b45b6.avif?t=1750723827\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras_big/320e35b207014ad99b4543c5f36b45b6.avif?t=1750723827 width=800 height=130 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Kill the Skeletons</strong> – <i>Embrace the Chaos!</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to fight the undead? <strong>Kill the Skeletons</strong> is a <strong>3D clicker battle</strong> where thousands of creatures fly across the battlefield, and hundreds of weapons unleash pure destruction!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Tap to Attack, Obliterate the Horde!</i></strong><br>Your reflexes and weapons are your greatest tools. Click to destroy waves of skeletons, buy more weapons and enjoy the chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/ebf19bf90ee4768db0b5c084e7a1abaf.poster.avif?t=1750723827\" width=640 height=273 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/ebf19bf90ee4768db0b5c084e7a1abaf.webm?t=1750723827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Thousands of Skeletons, Increasingly Tougher Star Levels!</i></strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt down thousands of skeletons and take on tougher star-level skeletons that are harder to kill but reward you with tons of gold! Grow your fortune and become unstoppable!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/e0f526871d31e990e8d48a45357daef2.poster.avif?t=1750723827\" width=640 height=273 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/e0f526871d31e990e8d48a45357daef2.webm?t=1750723827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Over 10 Unique Weapons</i></strong><br>From swords and magic casters to laser runes and giant mortars, each weapon has its own mechanics and stunning visual effects!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/253814a39fcfc915d96c7db51f25f99b.poster.avif?t=1750723827\" width=640 height=273 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/253814a39fcfc915d96c7db51f25f99b.webm?t=1750723827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Unlimited Upgrades</i></strong><br>There’s no limit to your power! <strong>Upgrade your weapons and combine them for greater star level weapons </strong>to take on even larger enemy swarms!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/8609de668dbea0c89c7cabfed06ea548.poster.avif?t=1750723827\" width=640 height=273 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3548990/extras/8609de668dbea0c89c7cabfed06ea548.webm?t=1750723827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Mini-Games & Permanent Upgrades</strong>!<br>The fun never stops! Play mini-games to earn rewards and unlock <strong>permanent upgrades</strong> for an even stronger start each time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Three Different Currencies, Three Unique Strategies</strong><br>Each currency has its own mechanics and upgrade paths, allowing you to customize your playstyle and maximize your power.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀💀💀 <br>The skeleton war is about to begin! <strong>Grab your weapons, control the chaos, and dominate the battlefield!</strong> <br>💀💀💀</p>",
